  (text "POWER TREE:\nVBUS (5V USB-C) → STPMIC1 → Buck (3.3V) → VDD_3V3\n                                   → LDO1 (1.8V) → VDD_1V8\n                                   → LDO2 (1.1V) → VDD_1V1\nVBAT_CR2032 (3V) → VBAT domain (backup)\n\nCURRENT BUDGET:\nVDD_3V3: STM32L562(15mA) + A71CH(3mA) + PN7150(40mA TX) + nRF52833(12mA TX) = ~70mA peak\nVDD_1V8: FPC1025(5mA) + nRF52833 IO(2mA) = ~7mA\nVDD_1V1: nRF52833 core(8mA) = ~8mA\nSTANDBY: STM32L562 STOP2(1.5µA) + A71CH(50µA) = ~51.5µA → 180 days on CR2032"
    (at 400 400 0) (uuid "txt0001"))

  (text "SECURITY NOTES:\n- All private keys stored in A71CH secure element (never leave chip)\n- STM32L562 TrustZone enabled (secure/non-secure partition)\n- RDP Level 2 in production (permanent SWD disable)\n- OTFDEnc for QSPI flash (on-the-fly decryption)\n- Fingerprint template storage in A71CH secure RAM\n- Firmware OTA signed with Ed25519 (public key in STM32 option bytes)"
    (at 400 500 0) (uuid "txt0002"))
